Text:
Very nice movie with the superstar in Kung Fu martial arts Jackie Chan. 
In this movie Jackie Chan impersonates a guy. A family tries to uphold 
their honor while keeping their Sacred Kung Fu book from getting into 
the wrong hands. A tale of deceit, mistrust, and traditional values 
unfolds, along with spectacular fight sequences necessary to keep the 
Snake-Crane Secret....!For more information go to 
wing-chunws/Snake%20and%20Crane.html
